      "english": "I sort of believe that unconditional love expressed through presence and respect is what matters most now.",
      "sourceAudio": "中级/B13.mp3",
      "sourceDocument": "中级/B13.docx",
      "day": 13,
      "daySentence": 17,
      "id": 257
